---
// Component Imports
import Page from "../layouts/Page.astro";
import Head from "../layouts/Head.astro";
import Hero from "../layouts/WorkHero.astro";
import mangesh from "../images/mangesh.png";
import mangeshFull from "../images/mangesh-lg.png";
import Modal from "../components/Modal.astro";
import ButtonIcon from "../components/ButtonIcon.astro";
import { Image, Picture } from "@astrojs/image/components";

const meta = {
  title: "Mangesh Thombare",
  description: "Portfolio website for a game designer.",
};
---

<Page>
  <Head slot="head" {meta} />
  <Hero />
  <main
    id="content-wrapper"
    class="container mx-auto py-6 px-8 md:py-24 md:px-0 lg:py-12 dark:bg-dark-900 dark:text-white"
  >
    <div
      class="container min-h-full space-y-12 my-2 text-left leading-relaxed px-4 lg:px-8"
    >
      <div
        id="pagination"
        class="bg-white flex flex-wrap space-x-2 rounded-1 shadow-md p-4 items-center dark:bg-dark-300"
      >
        <a
          href="/"
          class="hover:transition-all hover:ease hover:text-geraldine-500 hover:duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:border-b-4 focus:border-slate-500"
          tabindex="0">Home</a
        >
        <span class="h-6 w-6 i-solar:double-alt-arrow-right-line-duotone"
        ></span>
        <a
          href="/work/#content-wrapper"
          class="hover:transition-all hover:ease hover:text-geraldine-500 hover:duration-200 focus:outline-none focus:border-b-4 focus:border-slate-500"
          tabindex="0">Work</a
        >
        <span class="h-6 w-6 i-solar:double-alt-arrow-right-line-duotone"
        ></span>
        <a
          href="#"
          class="focus:outline-none focus:border-b-4 focus:border-slate-500"
          tabindex="0">Mangesh Thombare</a
        >
      </div>

      <div class="font-display my-6 text-f-xl fw600">
        Mangesh
        <span class="text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-300">Thombare</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start md:flex-row">
        <div
          class="flex border-2 border-gray-200 flex-shrink-0 shadow-lg my-4 mx-2 md:w-1/2 lg:w-auto dark:border-gray-800 hover:border-geraldine-400 dark:hover:border-geraldine-400"
        >
          <Image
            class="h-auto object-contain w-full dark:filter dark:brightness-75 dark:contrast-125"
            src={mangesh}
            alt="Mangesh Thombare"
            width={480}
            height={270}
          />
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4 my-4 px-2 md:pl-6">
          <p>
            This was a portfolio website project for a game designer. His
            requirements were a responsive website that showcased his CV,
            embedded videos, documents of his completed projects, and lastly, a
            contact form.
          </p>

          <ul class="list-inside list-decimal">
            <li>Portfolio website.</li>
            <li>Responsive design.</li>
            <li>Embedded videos and documents.</li>
            <li>Modal for images.</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div>
              <ButtonIcon
                id="modal3-trigger"
                color="bg-cyan-700 hover:bg-cyan-600 dark:hover:bg-cyan-500 cursor-pointer"
                iconClass="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-current i-solar:full-screen-square-line-duotone"
              >
                Screenshot
              </ButtonIcon>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="bg-white border rounded-md flex flex-col border-gray-200 shadow-md p-6 gap-4 justify-around sm:flex-row dark:bg-dark-700 dark:border-dark-600"
      >
        <div>
          <div
            class="rounded-full flex mx-auto border-gray-300 border-2 h-28 w-28 items-center justify-center md:mb-8 md:ml-12"
          >
            <span class="h-16 w-16 i-solar:user-hand-up-bold-duotone"></span>
          </div>

          <span
            class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 text-geraldine-600 w-10 i-ph:quotes-duotone md:h-12 md:w-12"
          ></span>

          <div class="space-y-3 px-4 md:px-8">
            <p>
              Akshay designed my portfolio website. The best part about working
              with him was that, I got a site fully customized and tailored to
              my needs. It is easy to navigate and works seamlessly on all
              platforms mobiles, tablets or PCs. When certain changes had to be
              made, they were delivered with precision within 24 hours of
              request. He has the patience to work at your pace every step of
              the way. You can have a fully personalized experience at an
              affordable price. It has been a pleasure working with Akshay.
            </p>

            <p class="text-right fw600">- Mangesh Thombare</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-shrink-0 items-end place-content-end">
            <span
              class="h-10 text-geraldine-600 w-10 i-ph:quotes-duotone md:h-12 md:w-12"
            ></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Modal triggerId="modal3-trigger" title="Mangesh Thombare">
    <div class="mt-3 grid place-content-center">
      <Picture
        class="dark:filter dark:brightness-75 dark:contrast-125"
        src={mangeshFull}
        alt="Mangesh Thombare Full Image"
        widths={[300, 450, 600]}
        sizes="(max-width: 768px) 300px, (max-width: 1024px) 450px, 600px"
        aspectRatio={1.24}
      />
    </div>
  </Modal>
</Page>
